name: Investor's Edge DAO
description: We're a community driven ecosystem empowering people to invest in assets & businesses, dually owning equity in their community & assisting entrepreneurs in gaining access to easy funding (for both startups and business expansion). We promote a symbiotic relationship being that the community owns a piece of EVERY INVESTMENT funded by the DAO, in turn creating a vested interest in the success of business & community.
payDisclosure: Join our community & instantly become a savvy investor, by owning a piece of EVERY asset & business funded by the DAO!
